{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: "Boring! Boring! So boring! Nanami's bored!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Lucia! Lu~ci~a! What mission do you have? Take Nanami with you!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'I do have a few missions on hand...', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Then bring Nanami with you and Nanami will shining finger them all to death!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'No, thank you. I can handle them on my own. You can remain on standby here at the base.', 4: '2'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory14.png'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: "Awww! That's no fun! Lee, do you have anything for Nanami to do?!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "I'm doing technical work, you're already helping by not coming over.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "You think I'm a dingus, don't you! Nanami will have you know that her databanks are filled with superhuman levels of mechanical knowledge!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "It's not a question of accrued knowledge, but the trouble that arises when you start attaching strange contraptions to every piece of equipment.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'What do you mean "strange contraptions"?! Nanami is enhancing the equipment!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "You dare say that making things you can't control is enhancing?", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Lee just didn't know how to use it.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "Anyway, I don't need an extra pair of hands here! Go bother someone else.", 4: '2'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory14.png'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: 'I guess this leaves Liv... Liv?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: "I'm sorry, but my remaining task is taking care of the paperwork, which will probably be mundane.", 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: "Hm, that doesn't sound fun at all.", 4: '1'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory14.png'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: "What should I do then? Nanami's going to rot in boredom!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Maybe I should just destroy the base.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Wait!', 3: '51', 4: "There's got to be something else you can do!", 5: '55'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: "Oh, Commandant, you're here.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: "Hm... I know! I won't destroy the base if... Commandant agrees to go on a date with Nanami!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: "Something else... wait, Commandant, you're here!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'I just got here.', 3: '58', 4: "I've been standing behind you this whole time.", 5: '64'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Hmm, the fact that Commandant only shows up at this hour means that Commandant has time to kill, just like Nanami!', 4: '1'}
{2: "I've got things to do in a bit.", 3: '60', 4: 'I do have time to kill today.', 5: '62'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: "I don't care. Commandant is going on a date with Nanami!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Then Commandant should go on a date with Nanami!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Is Commandant a ghost?!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'How is that possible...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Commandant must know how bored Nanami is, because Commandant cares so deeply about Nanami! So, go out on a date with me!', 4: '1'}
